description: Growing up is hard to do anywhere. Growing up ENCHANTED is even harder to do in the town of ANYWHERE! Join Olianna the baby sorceress and her family & friends as she tries to learn life's mundane lessons while practicing magic in a world of giants, trolls, and dragons! Lesson number one - enjoying the finer points of school; getting along with her sorceress mother and knightly father; and finally, last but not least, controlling her urges to kill her baby brother a.k.a. pain-in-the-butt, Anto!

And then came - the Bully! First day of school, in a classroom filled with diverse students like a giant, a troll, a prince, and more - and already Oli has a problem: a bully that won't leave her alone. What's a baby sorceress to do, especially when she's forbidden to use her magic? And whose advice will she take for a solution? Meanwhile, her father follows the "knightly" trio, Sammie, Kandu, and Copper, to the dragon's lair, with expected results. And, what's Olianna's baby brother Anto up to this time?

Oh no! Anto in the clutches of a fire-breathing dragon! Meanwhile, Olianna, Bradley, and Thomas reach the end of their hunt, encountering a group of dragons. But are they nice dragons or evil dragons?

How will Oli & the gang get out of their dragon-cornered predicament (Skipping school to hunt dragons sounded like a great idea at the time!) and will help from Anto, her father & the "knightly" trio make things better...or worse? And whose side is excitable Sebastian on? Find out in the action-packed conclusion to our first story arc - Fighting Bullies, Hunting Dragons!

Olianna and the gang's back in an all-new fantasy adventure for all-ages! Something sinister is awakened from the icy depths of the lake one morning. Still forbidden to use her magic, can Oli and her family & friends evade the sea-dragon's clammy clutches and escape death's siren call?
Another exciting issue of Growing Up Enchanted!
Another exciting issue of Growing Up Enchanted!
